---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="1112 KING RD | FORENSIC AUDIO ANALYSIS">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="timestamp">02:38:00 — 02:44:00 AM</div>
      <h1 class="glitch" data-text="FORENSIC AUDIO ANALYSIS">FORENSIC AUDIO ANALYSIS</h1>
      <h2 class="sub-glitch">1112 KING ROAD, MOSCOW, IDAHO</h2>
      
      <p class="thesis">
        Audio recorded by the 1112 King Road lightbulb camera contains multiple <strong>high-salience acoustic events</strong> 
        consistent with human distress vocalizations and physical impacts.
      </p>

      <p class="thesis-detail">
        Three independent open-source models (VGGish, BEATs, and LAION-CLAP) converge on the same timestamps, 
        identifying signatures of <span class="highlight">biological terror</span> and <span class="highlight">structural impact</span> 
        that deviate significantly from background noise.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="/methodology" class="btn btn-primary">HOW WE KNOW (METHODOLOGY)</a>
        <a href="/evidence" class="btn btn-secondary">SEE THE EVIDENCE</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>The Signal</h3>
      <p>Analysis of 150+ acoustic events isolated <strong>12 high-confidence anomalies</strong> that align with the forensic timeline.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>The Biology</h3>
      <p>Acoustic roughness analysis confirms modulation in the <strong>30-150Hz band</strong>, the unique signature of human screams.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>The Consensus</h3>
      <p>Multi-model triangulation reduces false positives. When <strong>3 different AIs agree</strong>, the probability of error drops near zero.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255,62,62,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .timestamp {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--accent-red);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-red);
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 4.5rem;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .sub-glitch {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin: 0 0 40px 0;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .thesis {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .thesis-detail {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 50px auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 15px 30px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-cyan);
    color: #000;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-cyan);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent-red);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-red);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-red);
    color: #000;
  }

  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto 80px auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(20,20,20,0.8);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 30px;
    text-align: center;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
    .features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cta-group { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
